      <title>印度克什米尔地区选举的利害关系是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/jammu-and-kashmir-elections-2024-india-s-only-muslim-majority-region-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五年前，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪剥夺了查谟和克什米尔地区七十年来享有的自治权，将该国唯一的穆斯林占多数的省份从一个邦降级为联邦控制的领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/jammu-and-kashmir-elections-2024-india-s-only-muslim-majority-region-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 13:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国首相抨击保守党抵制香港，呼吁与中国缓和关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-peer-slams-tory-boycott-of-hong-kong-urges-thaw-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党资深人士彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 指责前保守党政府未能与中国维持“适当的沟通渠道”，没有履行英国在香港的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-peer-slams-tory-boycott-of-hong-kong-urges-thaw-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:58:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
